title: The Internet is Having a Collective Panic Attack Over Beyoncé’s Grammys Performance
text:
The Internet is Having a Collective Panic Attack Over Beyoncé’s Grammys Performance by Dana Eisenberg | 9:19 pm, February 12th, 2017 
Beyoncé performed at tonight’s Grammy Awards and people were, not surprisingly insanely excited about it. Before she sang a single note, the Internet sent itself into a tizzy. And once she did open her mouth, it was absolute mayhem. The performance was a lot about Beyoncé’s pregnancy and motherhood in general. Watch the video above. 
Here’s some of what went on on Twitter. Buzzfeed, in particular was going nuts: BEYONCE IS COMING
